Create GP Job from existing URL

Source: R/geoprocessing-class.R
gp_job_from_url.Rd

Create GP Job from existing URL

Usage

gp_job_from_url(url, token = arc_token())

Arguments

url

the url of an existing geoprocessing job

token

default arc_token(). The token to be used with the job.

See also

Other geoprocessing: arc_form_params(), arc_gp_job, arc_job_status(), gp_params

Examples

if (interactive()) {
job_url <- "https://hydro.arcgis.com/arcgis/rest/services/Tools/Hydrology/GPServer/TraceDownstream/jobs/jfde67910074649e4a567f0adbb8af870"

gp_job_from_url(
  job_url,
  token = auth_user()
)
}
